{
  "stem": "868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "On the way, I noticed that the toilets which we were using, allowed to use-- and you couldn't just go to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "You had to tell the German guard that you wanted to, to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And he would wait until three, four, five, or six were ready to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "He would then bring you to the toilet, which was outside, wait for you to finish, and bring you back so that everyone was accounted for at all times.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "So going back and forth on two or three trips with the straw, I noticed that the toilets were very close to the outside wall.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Now that, that wall was quite high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And on top were four rows of barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And the idea started taking root that perhaps I could escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Preposterous as this may sound to you now, the idea of escaping from such a garrison, with such a high wall, surrounded entirely by Germans, was fantasy more than anything else.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But it was prompted by something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew this was a place where you don't want to be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that reinf--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
